description: Due to an earlier misunderstanding of Olympia`s vision, Carrie`s Sigilyph was first used to attack Professor Sycamore, Cosette and Sophie upon arrival to the Anistar Sundial. It was then used in a double battle alongside Carrie`s Sableye where it took on Ash`s Frogadier and Pikachu. Having dodged Pikachu`s Electro Ball it used Psywave in return, however it was eventually defeated by Pikachu`s Thunderbolt.
name: Symboler (Carrie)
